OL,3,CThree men killed in weekend collisions
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,FThree men who died in road collisions
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland at the weekend
OL,8,Fhave been named.
OL,10,FA total of five people were killed in
OL,11,Fcrashes across Saturday and Sunday.
OL,13,FTwo men who died in a collision in the
OL,14,FUpper Ballinderry area have been named
OL,15,Fas Malek Kerbache, 41, and Mateusz
OL,16,FProkopiuk, 31.
OL,18,FBoth men were from the Portadown area.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
