OL,3,CThree men killed in weekend collisions
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,FOfficers are continuing to investigate
OL,7,Fthe fatal collision between a
OL,8,Fmotorbike and a car on the Glenavy
OL,9,FRoad.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Dave Stewart said:
OL,12,F"The driver of the white Tesla Model
OL,13,FY, who died, has been named as Malek
OL,14,FKerbache.
OL,16,F"The motorcyclist on the black Honda
OL,17,FCBR 600, who died, has been named as
OL,18,FMateusz Prokopiuk.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
