OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1777406752
OL,3,CThree men killed in weekend collisions
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,F"A passenger in the Tesla was taken to
OL,7,Fhospital for treatment to their
OL,8,Finjuries, but has since been
OL,9,Fdischarged.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, a man who died following a
OL,12,Fsingle-vehicle collision in the
OL,13,FDerrycourtney Road area of Caledon on
OL,14,FSaturday evening has been named as
OL,15,FEmmet Potter.
OL,17,FOne person arrested in connection with
OL,18,Fthe investigation remains in police
OL,19,Fcustody.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
